ices differ in the number of settings you have control over. With some, you get fine control over bit rate and determining file sizes. Others only give you passing control, focusing more on easy video capture. These settings are important. Frame rate, bitrate and file size can make a big difference in your recording experience. We cover that more in the Improving Your Recording&#39;s Quality section below."]},"id":"eed26ea6-8c8d-4ad0-a283-97ac5d7cd72a","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/Ja8YrbQn3hqW4unzxmtPrM.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":false,"importSrc":"https://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/prod/large/52308-roxio-game-capture-box.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ja8YrbQn3hqW4unzxmtPrM.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"Ja8YrbQn3hqW4unzxmtPrM","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ja8YrbQn3hqW4unzxmtPrM.jpg","alt":""},"id":"e435bbf4-485e-4467-91ec-c97ca4505eb8","type":"image"},{"data":{"hawk":"{\"data-model-name\":\"Roxio Game Capture\", \"data-widget-type\":\"price\"}","linkText":"Visit Site","url":"http://www.anrdoezrs.net/click-5218229-10881860","specs":null,"subtitle":"","urlStyle":"button","review":{"rating":0,"url":"https://www.tomsguide.com/us/elgato-stream-deck,review-4513.html","name":"Roxio Game Capture","id":""},"noFollow":false,"title":"<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/us/elgato-stream-deck,review-4513.html\">Roxio Game Capture</a>","pros":["Empty List"],"cons":["Empty List"]},"id":"0a684d79-0371-42db-aa7d-30ca22b6c351","type":"buying-guide"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Roxio Game Capture focuses specifically on <a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/us/elgato-stream-deck,review-4513.html\">video game capture</a>. It provides a good balance between ease of use, quality and design. The hardware isn&#39;t particularly difficult to set up or use. It comes with software to edit videos and quickly upload them to the internet."]},"id":"979b84c5-a9ff-4d9a-94a8-1d3d850dbdff","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Bes